This is your crown may fall.

827
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:27,520
No.

828
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:29,920
(Saying whatever line comes to mind)
This is your Golden Dome cupcake.

829
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:32,840
(Sun Qian clears the challenge)
You did it.

830
00:22:32,840 --> 00:22:34,000
A crown may fall,

831
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,920
(Queen speech)
but the Golden Dome won't.

832
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,680
Amazing.

833
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:41,260
Congrats. You won the game.

834
00:22:41,260 --> 00:22:43,260
(Success)

835
00:22:43,560 --> 00:22:45,480
(Winning players can choose two perks)
This time, the perks

836
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,480
come with double surprises.

837
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:48,880
Please choose two freely

838
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:50,400
from the three perk cards.

839
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:52,240
Two?

840
00:22:53,160 --> 00:22:54,080
That's so nice.

841
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:55,080
From all the options,

842
00:22:55,080 --> 00:22:56,240
you can pick two.

843
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,880
(Two out of three perks being given)
Well, look at that.

844
00:22:58,520 --> 00:22:59,280
Chocolate.

845
00:22:59,280 --> 00:23:00,200
(Liu Yuning chooses Perfect Timing)

846
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:02,840
And the bun.

847
00:23:02,840 --> 00:23:03,600
(Soft bun)
Bread works.

848
00:23:03,600 --> 00:23:05,080
They seem to love bread every episode.

849
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:06,680
Today, they can eat it with chocolate.

850
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:08,100
(Ning is always so thoughtful)
Perfect. That works.

851
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:09,580
(Very pleased)

852
00:23:10,420 --> 00:23:11,700
(Choice paralysis)

853
00:23:11,920 --> 00:23:12,880
I'll take this one.

854
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:15,520
(Jin Jing chooses Model Body)
Tango and Berry Bowl.

855
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:16,260
These two.

856
00:23:16,260 --> 00:23:17,140
(Berry Bowl)

857
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:18,040
Let me see.

858
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:21,420
The first one.

859
00:23:21,740 --> 00:23:23,060
(Zhang Linghe chooses Perfect Timing)

860
00:23:23,080 --> 00:23:24,080
Well, look at that.

861
00:23:24,080 --> 00:23:25,120
That's chocolate, right?

862
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:26,840
Then...

863
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:28,080
Let me see the second one.

864
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:32,200
Crunchy jerky.

865
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:32,880
(Can't stop thinking about it)
I finished a whole jar.

866
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:33,360
Two.

867
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:34,400
One chocolate and one jerky.

868
00:23:34,660 --> 00:23:36,220
(Totally Linghe's thing)

869
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,200
Perfect.

870
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:39,200
I want a Berry Bowl.

871
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:40,280
(Ding Chengxin chooses
Berry Bowl)

872
00:23:40,280 --> 00:23:40,640
This one.

873
00:23:41,600 --> 00:23:42,360
I want this one.

874
00:23:42,460 --> 00:23:43,480
(Ding's careful pick)

875
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:44,280
Berry Bowl.

876
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,160
Okay, next.

877
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:50,640
So nice to squeeze. So handy.

878
00:23:50,800 --> 00:23:51,520
I want this.

879
00:23:52,280 --> 00:23:53,420
Bam Bam.

880
00:23:53,420 --> 00:23:54,580
(Bam Bam.
Two punches for you)

881
00:23:55,760 --> 00:23:56,240
Okay.

882
00:23:56,960 --> 00:23:58,760
I'll take Bam Bam first.

883
00:23:58,760 --> 00:23:59,220
Sounds good?

884
00:23:59,220 --> 00:24:00,260
