Quick decision)

885
00:24:00,280 --> 00:24:01,880
Bam Bam first.

886
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:02,800
(At the age to play)
Bam Bam.

887
00:24:02,800 --> 00:24:04,360
Then I'll get another one.

888
00:24:05,020 --> 00:24:06,380
(Too many good picks)

889
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:07,580
One...

890
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:09,700
(Brain loading)

891
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:12,280
Crunchy jerky.

892
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:14,920
Or one Bam Bam.

893
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:16,520
(Keyu wants everything)
Or Everybody Look at Me.

894
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:18,000
No!

895
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,880
Bam Bam
and Thunder Twin Blades.

896
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:20,680
(Thunder Twin Blades)

897
00:24:20,680 --> 00:24:21,320
Okay.

898
00:24:21,320 --> 00:24:21,760
It's settled.

899
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:22,440
(Just here to have fun)
It's settled.

900
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:24,280
Bam Bam is...

901
00:24:25,460 --> 00:24:26,340
(This is fun)

902
00:24:26,360 --> 00:24:28,600
Who can I give two punches to?

903
00:24:28,820 --> 00:24:29,520
(The bros just love playing)

904
00:24:29,520 --> 00:24:30,880
Watch my 72 tricks.

905
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:31,760
I'm a Freeloader.

906
00:24:31,760 --> 00:24:32,640
Guess Who I Am.

907
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,640
Here's a Like.

908
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,760
For You, I'd Turn Into a Werewolf.

909
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:38,220
I'll just go with food.

910
00:24:38,420 --> 00:24:41,260
(Nothing beats food)

911
00:24:42,560 --> 00:24:43,920
I want this fruit bowl.

912
00:24:44,140 --> 00:24:45,020
(Sun Qian chooses
Berry Bowl)

913
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:46,360
No worries.

914
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:47,640
(Great minds think alike)
Berry Bowl.

915
00:24:47,640 --> 00:24:48,320
That's the first one.

916
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:49,600
How many can we pick?

917
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:50,360
You can pick two.

918
00:24:55,940 --> 00:24:56,980
(One more peek)

919
00:24:57,040 --> 00:24:58,480
Then I'll get one chocolate too.

920
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,280
Well, look at that.

921
00:24:59,340 --> 00:24:59,550
(Perfect Timing)

922
00:24:59,550 --> 00:24:59,680
(Soft bun)

923
00:24:59,700 --> 00:24:59,910
(Model Body)

924
00:24:59,910 --> 00:25:00,060
(Berry Bowl)

925
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:00,520
(Perfect Timing
Crunchy jerky)

926
00:25:00,520 --> 00:25:00,950
(Bam Bam
Berry Bowl)

927
00:25:00,960 --> 00:25:01,160
(Perfect Timing)

928
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:01,300
(Berry Bowl)

929
00:25:01,300 --> 00:25:01,510
(Thunder Twin Blades)

930
00:25:01,510 --> 00:25:01,620
(Bam Bam)

931
00:25:01,660 --> 00:25:02,900
(The perks have all been
given to the players)

932
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:03,440
Food.

933
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,800
Food.

934
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:05,440
Qian Jinding.

935
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:06,600
Thanks.

936
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:08,480
I got one too.

937
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:09,720
(Everyone gets one)
He Yiwei.

938
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:11,120
He Yiwei's is...

939
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:12,040
What's that?

940
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:13,200
I picked berries too.

941
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:13,960
Who won today?

942
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:14,960
I got one.

943
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:15,960
I won.

944
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:17,280
I'm keeping this.

945
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:18,720
I'm taking this to play with.

946
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:20,880
Alright, let's refuel for now.

947
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:22,480
Next, we're heading to

948
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:23,360
