949
00:25:23,360 --> 00:25:25,800
to see what he's really up to.

950
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:27,120
(Let's keep investigating)
Can we take this to the boss' office?

951
00:25:27,120 --> 00:25:27,520
We can.

952
00:25:27,920 --> 00:25:28,680
Hold on to it.

953
00:25:28,680 --> 00:25:29,480
You might get scared and drop it later.

954
00:25:31,980 --> 00:25:32,980
(Thunder Twin Blades)

955
00:25:42,020 --> 00:26:23,580
(The Truth Season 4 Viewing Calendar)

956
00:26:40,330 --> 00:26:44,330
♪Come now, players all,
let the game of reason start♪

957
00:26:44,330 --> 00:26:48,770
♪Unlock each hidden trial,
let courage spark the dark♪

958
00:26:50,790 --> 00:26:54,950
♪Night falls slow, shadows grow,
the sleuth is lost inside the maze♪

959
00:26:54,950 --> 00:26:59,170
♪Figures pass, lanterns sparse,
dark currents drift without a trace♪

960
00:26:59,170 --> 00:27:02,940
♪Wind picks up, footsteps rush,
cold laughter swallowed by the dark♪

961
00:27:02,940 --> 00:27:07,050
